## Sidebar delete (Files + Models chips)

| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| UX | Trash icon on **right end** of chip; visible on row hover only; minimal icon |
| Scope | Files sidebar + Models sidebar only (not Detailed Analysis / RAG yet) |
| Backend | `DELETE /api/sessions/{id}/files/{file_id}` and `DELETE .../models/{model_id}` remove JSON from disk |
| Decoupling | Deleting a **file** does not break saved **models** (snapshot data lives in model JSON) |
| DCF draft delete | Also removes linked computed `dcf` twin (`draft_id`) |
| Selection | If deleted item was open, clear main panel selection |

## Global pointer cursor

Interactive elements use `cursor: pointer` via `frontend/src/index.css` (`button`, `a`, `select`, `label[for]`, etc.). Text inputs keep `cursor: text`.
